description: Great value! With one parking space, central air conditioning & a common roof deck with 360 views, this home is in one of Southie's most coveted locations around the corner from restaurants, bars, shopping & the beach. This penthouse condo has high ceilings and lots of windows, providing ample natural light with city & water views. It has great closet space plus a storage cubby in the basement. The living room has a bay of windows & gorgeous marble decorative fireplace, and opens to the kitchen with granite counters and stainless appliances. A cleverly designed breakfast bar connects the kitchen and living room. Legally a 2 bedroom unit, this condo is currently an oversized 1 bedroom with a massive bedroom. Both entry doors & closets remain so it is easy to convert back to a 2 bedroom creating a 14x10 room and a 14x9 room, or enjoy it as is with plenty of space for a home office or Peloton. Nice full bathroom with a tub with shower. Professionally managed with healthy reserves.
